      *OET do file
*By Phil Tian
*version 11.2

clear all

set mem 250m
set maxvar 32000
set matsize 2000
set more off

cd E:/

capture log close
log using "OET_log", replace
use oetaug2010_pitstoplevel_v8.dta, clear

gen double ps=psexpectation/1000
gen double y=ln(ps+0.0000001/(1-ps+0.0000001))

program define OET_ML
args lnf gamma fn tao

tempvar M

gen double `M'= y/`gamma'- winpc - `fn'


quietly replace `lnf'=ln(normalden(`M'))-ln(`gamma')

end

ml model lf OET_ML (gamma:y=lap winpc_r bet earnings sdwin shistakes slostakes swealth  gender age BMI china aussie malay international* weekinc_1 weekinc_2 weekinc_3 wealth_1 wealth_2 perfuni totalprpayout schooling lefthand smoke englishspeaker maritalstatus experiment ) (fn:lap winpc_r bet earnings sdwin shistakes slostakes swealth  gender age BMI china aussie malay international* weekinc_1 weekinc_2 weekinc_3 wealth_1 wealth_2 perfuni totalprpayout schooling lefthand smoke englishspeaker maritalstatus experiment ), technique(nr)

ml check
ml search
ml maximize, difficult
ml graph
